---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services | Achillea Built">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl py-12 sm:py-16">

    <div class="mb-12 reveal">
      <h1 class="mb-6">Services</h1>
      <p class="text-lg leading-8 max-w-2xl">
        Achillea Built provides small-scale residential construction and repair,
        typically ranging from $500 to $15,000.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-7 max-w-2xl">
        Projects are approached with the same care and attention to detail you’d
        expect from larger construction work — just without the overhead or
        unnecessary complexity.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-10">

      <!-- Repairs -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Repairs & Improvements</h2>
        <p class="leading-7 mb-3">
          Thoughtful repair work that addresses root issues, not just surface symptoms.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Dry rot and exterior repairs</li>
          <li>Door and window adjustments or replacement</li>
          <li>Interior fixes and updates</li>
          <li>General home improvements</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Remodels -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Small Remodels</h2>
        <p class="leading-7 mb-3">
          Targeted remodel work where layout, finish, and execution all matter.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Bathroom updates</li>
          <li>Kitchen improvements and upgrades</li>
          <li>Interior reconfiguration</li>
          <li>Finish carpentry and trim work</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Exterior -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Exterior Structures & Site Work</h2>
        <p class="leading-7 mb-3">
          Durable, well-built exterior work designed for long-term use.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Fencing and gates</li>
          <li>Gravel pads, driveways, and site prep</li>
          <li>Deck repairs and small builds</li>
          <li>Outbuildings and utility structures</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Carpentry -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Finish & Detail-Oriented Work</h2>
        <p class="leading-7 mb-3">
          Clean, precise work where fit and finish make a difference.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Custom shelving and built-ins</li>
          <li>Trim and finish carpentry</li>
          <li>Woodwork and detail upgrades</li>
          <li>Installation of finished materials</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 reveal">
      <h2 class="mb-4">A Good Fit</h2>
      <p class="leading-7 mb-4 max-w-2xl">
        Achillea Built is a good fit for homeowners who want quality work,
        clear communication, and a thoughtful approach to construction without
        paying for a large contractor’s overhead.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-7 max-w-2xl">
        If your project is small to mid-sized but still deserves careful execution,
        it’s likely a good match.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 reveal">
      <a href="/estimate" class="btn btn-lg sm:min-w-56">
        Request an Estimate
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>